# ============================================================================
#  CS 1.6 Pi server -- allowlist .gitignore
#
#  Philosophy: track only what YOU customize. Everything stock (AMX Mod X
#  source tree, language files, gamedata, binaries, maps) is re-fetched by
#  setup.sh and is intentionally NOT tracked.
#
#  Tracked:
#    - repo scaffolding (README, scripts, .gitignore)
#    - configs/*.cfg, *.ini, *.txt           (your server configs)
#    - addons/amxmodx/configs/*              (your plugin list, amxx.cfg, etc.)
#    - addons/amxmodx/plugins/*.amxx         (compiled plugins you run)
#    - addons/metamod/plugins.ini            (which MM plugins load)
#  Never tracked:
#    - users.ini (admin SteamIDs), *.toml (FRP token), ban lists
#    - binaries (.so/.dll/.dat/.mmdb), maps/sounds/models/sprites
#    - the stock scripting/, data/lang/, data/gamedata/ trees
#    - logs
# ============================================================================

# 1) Ignore everything at the repo root
/*

# 2) Re-allow repo scaffolding
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/setup.sh
!/update.sh
!/sync-to-repo.sh
!/start_cs.sh
!/configs/
!/addons/

# 3) configs/ -- text configs only
!configs/**/
!configs/**/*.cfg
!configs/**/*.ini
!configs/**/*.txt

# 4) addons/ -- re-allow ONLY the specific subfolders we customize.
#    (We do NOT blanket re-allow addons/**/ , so stock trees like
#     scripting/ and data/ are never descended into.)
!addons/amxmodx/
!addons/amxmodx/configs/
!addons/amxmodx/plugins/
!addons/metamod/

# 5) Re-allow the file types we care about inside those folders
!addons/amxmodx/configs/*.ini
!addons/amxmodx/configs/*.cfg
!addons/amxmodx/plugins/*.amxx
!addons/metamod/*.ini

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  Hard exclusions (last = wins). Belt-and-suspenders even though the folders
#  above aren't re-allowed.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Stock AMX Mod X trees (re-fetched by setup.sh, never our customization)
addons/amxmodx/scripting/
addons/amxmodx/data/
addons/amxmodx/modules/
addons/amxmodx/dlls/
addons/amxmodx/configs/users.ini
addons/amxmodx/configs/user.ini
**/*.so
**/*.dll
**/*.dat
**/*.mmdb
**/logs/**
*.log
*.toml
banned.cfg
listip.cfg
